entry.title: ypujante/imgui-raylib-cmake
entry.summary: This is a 100% self-contained "Hello World" project for an ImGui application that uses raylib for the backend, CMake for the build and Google Angle on macOS (to use the Metal API instead of the deprecated OpenGL API)
